column4: Dubai transport authority agrees to buy 200 Tesla vehicles
column5: DUBAI  Feb 14 Dubai's Road & Transport Authority (RTA) said on Tuesday it has agreed to buy 200 electric vehicles from Tesla Inc  a day after the carmaker announced it would open its first Middle East office in Dubai.
